Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}豹のように美しいくわたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:18.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}着飾るは闇の毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:24.18,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}谷間の百合　踏みつけても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:29.80,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの場所に向かうため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:35.99,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}牙を立てる果肉の甘さは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:42.25,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}結ばぬ実の不実の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.81,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}交わりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.01,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}逃げてるのか追ってるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.73,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}わからなくなるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}わたしを視て　もっと深く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.07,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}溺れ乱れ蜜地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.00,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}魔触の爪　腐蝕の骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.70,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}軋む音響かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.15,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}これが愛か憎しみなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.07,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}答えは必要ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:14.69,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}ああ捕まれた心臓は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:21.04,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの氷のような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:27.47,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)\be1}指の中で生き返るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}如同豹一般美麗無比的我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:18.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}裝扮在身的是黑暗的毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:24.18,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使不惜踐踏過山澗的百合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:29.80,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}也是為了前往你的所在之處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:35.99,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}能讓人倒牙般甘甜鮮美的果肉是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:42.25,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}未成熟果實的不真實的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.81,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}混雜在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.01,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}是否要逃避呢　抑或去追趕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.73,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}連我自己都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}請注視著我吧　更加深邃一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.07,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}便沉溺混亂於甜蜜地獄中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.00,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}魑魅魍魎之爪　腐蝕了的骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.70,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}吱嘎搖曳之聲在迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.15,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}這究竟是愛呢　抑或會是憎恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.07,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}還有必要回答這個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:14.69,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}啊　那顆被揪住的心臟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:21.04,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在你的那極度冰冷無比的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:27.47,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)\be1}手指中再一次起死而回生了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.15,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}光を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:36.89,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}舞い散る花の香りは甘く囁く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:47.53,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}繰り返される終わりのない綻びは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:56.04,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}小さな傷跡さえ　癒せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:01.42,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}悲しみの輪　重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:04.84,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの手　あなたの声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:11.21,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの面影を　求めても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:15.56,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}遠い　ドアは　開くことなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.93,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}問いかけた命の意味　空しくあの空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.64,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}木霊して　響くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.30,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}永遠の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.15,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}光芒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:36.89,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}飛落的花朵散發出淡淡的幽香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:47.53,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}一直反覆著　永無終結地綻放著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:56.04,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使是小小的傷痕　也不能得到治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:01.42,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}悲傷之輪　再度旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.84,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使渴望著你的手　你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:11.21,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}甚至是你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:15.56,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}也仍舊無法打開遠處的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.93,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}向那片空虛的天空　追尋生命的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.64,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}迴響起的只是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.30,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}名為「永遠」的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是薔薇少女的第一人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人他不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  你能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  真的是薔薇少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp160}　{\fsp1}Rosa Mystica\N{\r}你從父親大人那裡得到薔薇聖母了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就展開攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是第一人偶  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  薔薇少女第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得可真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我叫莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是哪裡不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  真紅  她會不會有些怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶中也不乏內向的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總感覺有些彆扭  雪白雪白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要解決掉她了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在尋找父親之前還有你必須要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  似乎有個男人為了尋找她們而來到了這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還說會給協助尋找的人一定的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定又是哪個王公貴族的消遣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  全灑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右  左
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  你能辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對水銀燈那麼好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行嗎？！  她也是薔薇少女不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是必須要打倒她才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻每天都在幫助她練習走路  沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉  那個人偶很乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼嘛  突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常的優美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人會不會為此而高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會對我微笑嗎  會擁抱我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有假吧  絕對？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不假  因為你的確如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓父親大人早點見到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到我…  行走的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  真紅  多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這都是你自己努力的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  這份感激我該如何表達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  真的謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再練習一會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪會有活人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這戒指可真美麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聲不吭就觸碰女士  真是失禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠然  真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在道歉之餘  我能拜見一下您的閨房嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真遺憾  打擾你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎並不在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  那個男人就回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過他是怎麼知道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可對誰都沒說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕  是人偶師…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶師？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  一定是夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被丟棄了  然後看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被父親擁抱著的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢  那只是你做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  準備吃早餐吧  莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的記憶正在逐漸恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  人偶師也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Lempicka\N{\r}琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  正好來做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在愛麗絲遊戲中  如果不打倒所有的人就無法見到父親大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你戰勝了蒼星石  但若仍這樣留著水銀燈那還有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好待她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頂惹人厭的帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我從父親大人那裡得到的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能夠進入我的n之領域…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  別傷害真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫水銀燈  是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  似乎通過鏡子來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我是水銀燈  是薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  薔薇少女第一人偶水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話  退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是愛麗絲遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  全聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知情也就不必多費口舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部…  是空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是未完成的人偶半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是僅憑著對父親的思念而行動的可憐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擁有薔薇聖母  總有一天會消失的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…  那不是真的  不是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是薔薇少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人製作的  第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不去莎拉那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓你作為人偶幸福地生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了那麼多的努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能作為人偶和莎拉一起過著幸福的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  已經死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！  救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！ 真紅！ 救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不在最初告訴她事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能對她說「你是見不到父親的」嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得那樣總比說謊要好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  不是薔薇少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個半成品…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  為什麼會創造出我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會創造出這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為愛著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟是為何而生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  蒼星石也趕快…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我還沒與真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再給媒介增加負擔了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石和蒼星石都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成為一個出色的淑女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吃驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很吃驚呢  因為明明發生了那種事還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  果然是薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人認同了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇聖母就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事  怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我能夠挺起胸膛說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是水銀燈  薔薇少女第一人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  你怎麼會是薔薇少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  你還未完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是可憐的人偶半成品…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女  是以究極的少女愛麗絲為目標製作出來的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  和我們不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直是用這種眼光來看待我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為我是比你劣等的可憐人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我的溫柔話語以及援助之手  都只是在可憐我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了讓自己高高在上的優越感得以滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想要一邊讓自己更為高貴更為父親所寵愛  一邊嘲弄著我  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個討厭的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是被生的有點得天獨厚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是偶爾被製作得還不錯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說  我的存在只是為了用來提高你自身的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！  我只是希望至少能讓你和莎拉一起幸福地生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不正是在玩弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有認同我是薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的人偶沒可能成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為愛麗絲的  將會是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都深愛著父親大人的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會成為愛麗絲  接受父親大人的擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受父親大人的關懷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才會得到的父親的寵愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱著你  注視著你  父親大人深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這些幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來打破吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人深愛著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正深愛著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從父親大人那裡得到的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿著父親大人的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明明是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半成品…廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都有終結之時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石和蒼星石  都已入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅也已解除契約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時代的愛麗絲遊戲已然結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待將留給下一個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個胸針…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥冥
